body_html:
I tried with Amazon Linux and was able to build the commit 7d3884b,

The AMI I use is ami-0ff8a91507f77f867. The bazel was installed from Federa COPR (epel 7): https://docs.bazel.build/versions/master/install-redhat.html

Maybe you could try again with a fresh EC2 instance and see if the issue still exist?
